# Bookstore-Revenue-Inventory_Management-analysis
# 📚 Bookstore Revenue & Inventory Management Analysis (SQL)

## 📖 Project Overview

This project demonstrates SQL-based analysis of a bookstore database using PostgreSQL. It focuses on managing books, customers, and orders while generating meaningful business insights through SQL queries.

The project includes database creation, table relationships, data cleaning, and analytical queries to evaluate sales performance, customer purchasing behavior, inventory status, and revenue generation.

---

## 🎯 Objectives

- Design a relational bookstore database
- Import and manage bookstore data
- Establish relationships using Primary & Foreign Keys
- Perform data validation and cleaning
- Solve real-world business problems using SQL
- Generate business insights for decision-making

---

